
* Setup for Ikarus

    cd /usr/local/lib/ikarus

    bzr branch lp:~ikarus-libraries-team/ikarus-libraries/srfi

    cd

    git clone git://github.com/dharmatech/agave.git

    echo export IKARUS_LIBRARY_PATH=`pwd`/agave >> ~/.bashrc

* Setup for Ypsilon

    cd

    git clone git://github.com/dharmatech/agave.git

    echo export YPSILON_SITELIB=`pwd`/agave >> ~/.bashrc

* Run a demo on Ypsilon

    cd agave/demos

    ypsilon flexi-line.scm

* Run a demo on Ikarus

    cd agave/demos

    ikarus --r6rs-script flexi-line.scm

